<body>
    <section class="hero">
    <div class="info-box top-left">
      <strong>📲 Scan to Simplify</strong><br>
      Say goodbye to standing in long lines. Just scan and track your spot with ease!
    </div>

    <div class="info-box top-right">
      <strong>🛡️ Secure & Instant</strong><br>
      End-to-end encrypted QR scanning. Your privacy is always protected.
    </div>

